:\/\/docs.google.com\/forms\/d\/1hYTKP4B66TffJL7cZyed7UEwoNPMwlR9d1szdJzT7fw\/edit?usp=forms_home&amp;ths=true\">competition form<\/a> by Wednesday 7th August <\/li><li>Avoid animal heads or otherwise non-humanoid shapes (extra arms, legs, etc)&nbsp;<\/li><li>Your image must not include copyright or trademark-protected content, or content that infringes any third-party\u2019s publicity rights<\/li><li>Your image must not include religious references or symbols, and must not include content that is obscene, pornographic, libelous or otherwise objectionable (including, without limitation, profanity or offensive language) as determined by Company in its sole discretion<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Once the entry period is over, a panel of judges here at NaturalMotion will create a short list of our favourites based on originality, creativity and fit to the contest theme. We\u2019ll start a series of polls on Facebook to allow you to have the ultimate say over which Titan design should win!&nbsp; The winner will be selected based on number of votes received.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Later in the year we\u2019ll open the\nsecond stage of Design A Titan, where you\u2019ll get to decide the skills, resist\nand put the finishing touches on our Titan. We\u2019ll then aim to run a special\nCommunity Event in early 2020 featuring our Community Titan!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><br><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> The Prizes<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><br>\n<strong>1st Place<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Your design will be immortalised in Dawn of Titans!<\/li><li>Free 4* version of your Titan when it releases<\/li><li>60,000 Gems<\/li><li>Signed Dawn of Titans poster<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Runners Up<\/strong> <strong>\/ Short Listed Finalists<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Free 4* Version of the Titan when it releases<\/li><li>30,000 Gem<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Prizes will be delivered within 10 days of the completion of the contest.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The fine print:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>By subm